dialogue: So anyway... I'm sure you want to see what's behind me. But, if I'm honest it's a little perilous.
It's not that I don't want you to go, but... well, I don't really trust that you'll be fine.
Well, if you really want to come in, I'll have to have some sort of requirment. HMM something original...
OH! Ok how about, you come back after you've broke a bunch of glass jars. There's some around here.
If you can break a bunch of glass jars I think I'll let you in.
